---
title: Crispy Falafel Crumble Hummus Plates with Herby Roasted Veggies and Flatbreads
description: We've brought the flavours of the Mediterranean to this plant-based dinner! Garlicky flatbread wedges, roasted veggies and crispy falafel all sit on a bed of creamy hummus. A garlicky cream sauce comes in clutch to finish off this delicious plate.
